# NER 實作練習
- Author: Lynn

- Reference:

### 以 NLTK 進行英文文本的 NER

import nltk  #若使用Jupyter notebook 可能要 !pip install nltk
nltk.download('punkt')
nltk.download('averaged_perceptron_tagger')
nltk.download('maxent_ne_chunker')
nltk.download('words')

import pandas as pd

from nltk.tokenize import word_tokenize ##做tokenize 斷詞
from nltk.tag import pos_tag #做詞性標註
from nltk import ne_chunk   #NER aka 命名實體識別

#1.Tokenize
#斷詞請使用 word_tokenize
sentence = 'Tom Hanks is an American actor and filmmaker.'

tokenized_sentence = word_tokenize(sentence) 
print(f'tokenized_sentence: {tokenized_sentence}\n')

#詞性標註
tagged_sentence = pos_tag(tokenized_sentence)  
#注意: pos_tag會將接收到的變數以分割的str為單位做標示詞性，若pos_tag(sentence)，因傳入的變數sentence只有一段1string(原句子)，
#所以pos_tag會產出以每個字母，標點符號為單位的標示詞性的list，且list中每個element為tuple， ex, [('T', 'NNP'), ('o', 'MD'), ('m', 'VB'), (' ', 'NNP')...]
print(f'tagged_sentence: {tagged_sentence}\n')


#NER aka 命名實體識別
named_entities = ne_chunk(tagged_sentence)
print(f'named_entities: {named_entities}')

text:
tokenized_sentence: ['Tom', 'Hanks', 'is', 'an', 'American', 'actor', 'and', 'filmmaker', '.']

tagged_sentence: [('Tom', 'NNP'), ('Hanks', 'NNP'), ('is', 'VBZ'), ('an', 'DT'), ('American', 'JJ'), ('actor', 'NN'), ('and', 'CC'), ('filmmaker', 'NN'), ('.', '.')]

named_entities: (S
  (PERSON Tom/NNP)
  (ORGANIZATION Hanks/NNP)
  is/VBZ
  an/DT
  (GPE American/JJ)
  actor/NN
  and/CC
  filmmaker/NN
  ./.)

# PosTag後顯示 NNP VBZ JJ什麼意思?

NNP = Proper noun, singular_專有名詞
***
VBZ = Verb, 3rd person singular present
***
JJ = adj
***
More:

https://www.ling.upenn.edu/courses/Fall_2003/ling001/penn_treebank_pos.html

# NER

NER評價指標

NER本質上包含兩個子任務：邊界檢測和類型識別，一般認為一個實體識別正確，需要該實體的邊界與類型都正確。

##功能
输入，“小丽去深圳参加了腾讯公司的面试”。

那么输出为，“小丽/人名 去 深圳/地名 参加了 腾讯公司/组织 的面试”。

##NER 分類

![20210505214217792.png](data:image/png;base64,)

# 練習 
**Hint:Tokenize -> PosTag -> NER**
***
txt ='"Welcome to Barbados, Tobdy!"
print(ne_chunk(pos_tag(word_tokenize("Welcome to Barbados, Tobdy!"))))
### 以 SpaCy 進行'英文'文本的 NER (重要)
2015年開發的強大套件

#method with string module
import spacy
import string #非必要 方便而已
nlp = spacy.load("en_core_web_sm")
sentence = 'Tom Hanks is an American actor and filmmaker.'
type(string.punctuation)
print(string.punctuation)

for c in sentence:  
    if c in string.punctuation:  # string.punctuation =  !"#$%&'()*+,-./:;<=>?@[\]^_`{|}~
        sentence = sentence.replace(c,'')  
print(sentence) #回傳無標點符號的string

doc = nlp(sentence) #一個句子就是一個文本，裡頭放了8個文本(element)
print('辨識結果：\n')
for ent in doc.ents:
    print(f'{ent.text}:{ent.label_}')

#輸出string 的result

Tom Hanks is an American actor and filmmaker

Tom Hanks:PERSON
American:NORP

#method 2 ->

import spacy
import string
nlp = spacy.load("en_core_web_sm")  #載入適用於中小型英文text檔的spacy module

sentence = 'Tom Hanks is an American actor and filmmaker.'
for c in sentence:  
    if c in string.punctuation:  # string.punctuation =  !"#$%&'()*+,-./:;<=>?@[\]^_`{|}~
        sentence = sentence.replace(c,'') #回傳無標點符號的string  




doc = nlp(sentence)
#ents = list(doc.ents)  #result: [Tom Hanks, American] (沒必要轉list，因為for x in XXX, XXX的位置都吃)
ents = doc.ents      #result: (Tom Hanks, American)

#error:   [x.label_ for x in ent ]  x是token 沒有attribute .label_ 
entities=[(i.text,i.label_) for i in ents]
#得到[('Tom Hanks', 'PERSON'), ('American', 'NORP')] 此為list中有turple

for x in entities:
  x = ':'.join(x);
  print (x);

# Trail 1 #善用token 的 .i .text .pos_ .pos .dep_  
#若要一次看清楚  doc中有很多token
#且 doc.label_ (token 沒有.label_)
for token in doc:
  token_item  = token.i


  token_text = token.text
  token_pos = token.pos_ 
  token_dep = token.dep_
  print(f'{token_item<10}:{token_text:<10}:{token_pos:<10}:{token_dep:<10}')

"""比較
for ent in doc.ents:
    print(f'{ent.text}:{ent.label_}')

from ltp import LTP

sentence = '在台北閒晃散步，發現蔣渭水紀念公園，原來首善之都內竟有紀念這位與孫中山同等地位的革命前輩之處'
#sentence = '為紀念里奧納度·達文西逝世五百年，巴黎羅浮宮博物館舉辦一場大型展覽，展出這位佛羅倫斯畫家、藝術創作者的作品。'

# 預設下載 Small 模型
ltp = LTP()

#seg 為編號 hidden詞本身 
segment, hidden = ltp.seg([sentence]) #分詞 Tokenize
pos = ltp.pos(hidden) #詞性標註PosTag -> 對NER很重要 (但此套件的寫法不用傳pos)
ner = ltp.ner(hidden) #實體識別NER

#print(segment)
#print(hidden)
#print(pos)
#print(ner)


#若要批次處理 在外面多加一詞迴圈
for ent in ner[0]: #第0句處理
    tag = ent[0]
    idx_start = ent[1]
    idx_end = ent[2]+1   
    print(segment[0][idx_start:idx_end],tag)
        #segment此為變數名稱 裝分詞結果  
        #(segment[0][idx_start:idx_end] -> 詞本身
        #tag) -> 類別/詞性

source: ## 以科技橘報『AI』報導為例

# 安裝套件
!pip install wordcloud

# 下載台北思源黑體，並命名taipei_sans_tc_beta.ttf
!wget -O taipei_sans_tc_beta.ttf https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1eGAsTN1HBpJAkeVM57_C7ccp7hbgSz3_&export=download

# 讀檔
import pandas as pd

csv = '/content/drive/MyDrive/shared_folder/dataset/techorange_ai.csv'
df = pd.read_csv(csv)

titles = df['title'].apply(str).tolist()
contents = df['content'].apply(str).tolist()

total_articles = df.shape[0]
print(f'共{total_articles}篇文章')

# 專有名詞識別
from ckiptagger import WS, POS, NER

#產生物件
ws = WS("./data")
pos = POS("./data")
ner = NER("./data")

sentences = []
for i in range(total_articles):
    sentence = titles[i] + '。' + contents[i]
    #sentence = titles[i]
    sentences.append(sentence)

tokens = ws(sentences)   #2D  = was(1D)
postags = pos(tokens)    #postags = pos(2D)
entities = ner(tokens,postags)

# 取出專有名詞
all_entities = []
for ent_set in entities:
    for ent in ent_set:
        #print('%s %s' % (ent[2],ent[3]))
        all_entities.append(ent[3]) #此turple有4個 ent[3]為詞本身

print(len(all_entities))

# 計算次數(詞頻)
from collections import Counter

ct = Counter(all_entities)  #ct詞頻
print(ct.most_common())

# 產生文字雲
from wordcloud import WordCloud
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

wc = WordCloud(background_color='white',
               max_words=200,
               font_path='/content/taipei_sans_tc_beta.ttf',
               mask=None)
wc.generate_from_frequencies(ct)
plt.imshow(wc)

# 儲存文字雲圖檔
wc.to_file('/content/drive/MyDrive/shared_folder/cloudword_ner.png')
